<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I got this lense yesterday.  I went to runny eye in hopes of getting a group so I could do the crafted armor.  Anyway I zoned in from the Gorge and did /who.  I was the only person in there.  Before I could take a step, Broxx came around the corner and was right in front of me.  As I zone I got a message saying Broxx has changed focus.  In the Gorge, the only other player was a 54 Pally.  I offered him 100pp to kill Broxx.  He did, with little effort, let me have lense and did not charge me :).  Anyway my point for posting is the fact that Broxx was at the entrace on his own, no people when in dungeon, so I don't think he was trained.</font></td></tr></table>
