<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>My group killed Borxx twice last night with very little trouble.  Both time, she wandered up top on her own.  The first time, there were some higher levels around who helped, but the second time, it was just us.  29 cleric, 28 ranger, 27 warrior, and 2 26 shamen.  The interesting part, is that the second time it was really only 3 taking her on.  As we engaged, the cleric went LD and 1 shaman got too close to the zone line and ended up in Misty.  By the time he got back, the other shaman had gotten to close and zoned.  The warrior and I (the ranger) were both down to about half hp.<BR>
Maybe it was a fluke, I don't know, but we felt pretty good, sicne Borxx was red to me at 28.<BR>
<BR>
Now we need to kill her 3 more times so everyone in the group can get a staff...<BR>
<BR>
Daruin<BR>
28 Ranger<BR>
